"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-10-12-celine-dion-row-erupts-claims-olympics-show-pre-recorded-21782774\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Celine Dionstunned the world when she returned to the stage almost two years after announcing herstiff-person syndromediagnosis.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 128, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But insiders are now claiming herOlympic Gamesopening ceremony set was pre-recorded.\", \"from\": 129, \"to\": 213, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 56-year-old Canadian-born singer moved fans withher performance of French singer \\u00c9dith Piaf's Hymne \\u00e0 L'amour (Hymn to Love)in front of the Eiffel Tower in July.\", \"from\": 215, \"to\": 380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999279217020314, \"rank\": 7.124102364433309e-05, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 300, \"end\": 310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\", \"score\": 0.9999999997958184, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"\\u00c9dith Piaf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marking her first performance since 2020 and the first since going public with her diagnosis,social mediaexploded with praise, and French PresidentEmmanuel Macroncalled it the 'emotional highlight' of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 513, \"end\": 519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999279217020314, \"rank\": 7.124102364433309e-05, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Celine, 56, is now facing claims that her performance was 'without a shadow of a doubt' pre-recorded after music experts spoke toLiberationnewspaper for an article titled 'Did Celine Dion lip-sync during the Olympic opening ceremony?'\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Choosing to remain anonymous, a sound engineer spoke to the outlet, where they claimed: 'It was 100% playback, you can hear it from the first notes.'\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Classical pianist and musician Etienne Gu\\u00e9reau also weighed in on the matter, telling the respected news outlet: 'What we heard on TV was a corrected playback.'\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1154, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to the music industry sources, a musician with 25 years of experience, known onYouTubeas Wings of Pegasus, believes the performance sounded the same as Celine's rehearsal.\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1339, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He said the problem with this is that it is technically impossible, as songs will often have disparities even if they are performed by the same person.\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1492, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Celine has not issued a statement regarding the claims.\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1549, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The report upset fans, who were quick to defend the five-timeGrammywinner.\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One fan called the star's performance 'admirable regardless'.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1687, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'You do not have more important information to repeat?\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1743, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What is this need to tarnish, to denigrate?\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1787, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We do not care!\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1803, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You will not take away the emotion we felt at that moment.\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1862, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Celine Dion's vocal performance is admirable regardless.'\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1920, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1863, \"end\": 1874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0761657271199043e-47, \"text\": \"Celine Dion\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McyLuce wrote.\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1935, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kristina Adams wrote: 'Who cares - she was great either way'.\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1998, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1937, \"end\": 1945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristina_Davis\", \"score\": 0.9996672246258329, \"rank\": 0.00033288615041604633, \"text\": \"Kristina\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristina_Davis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristina_Davis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One fan, Tostitwo, referenced her health battle and said, 'She's sick, let her lip sync.'\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2089, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It comes after thestar, known for her songs like My Heart Will Go On and I am Alive, released herPrime Videodocumentary detailing her battle with the life-altering illness.\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2263, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Director Irene Taylor spoke to Metro.co.uksoon before its release, admitting that some scenes were 'unbearable' to film, particularly the momentCeline's foot began to spasm, leading to her entire body seizing up while experts rushed to her aid.\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2274, \"end\": 2286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irene_Taylor\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Irene Taylor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irene_Taylor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irene_Taylor\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As her seizure progressed, the mother of three was screaming in pain as her medical team worked to slow her symptoms.\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2628, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The hardest moment to film, the hardest moment to just be in the room with, was when she had her medical episode,' Irene said.\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2757, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2746, \"end\": 2751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irene_of_Athens\", \"score\": 0.5507297084731365, \"rank\": 0.8157722590256627, \"text\": \"Irene\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irene_of_Athens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irene_of_Athens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'That went on for quite a long time, between 40 minutes and an hour, depending on where you call it beginning and ending.\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's about five minutes in the film.\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 2917, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'That was almost unbearable.\", \"from\": 2919, \"to\": 2947, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I let my intellect kick in, and my director of photography and I, we ploughed through it, I would say.\", \"from\": 2948, \"to\": 3054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'That was very difficult, certainly the most extraordinarily unpleasant and extraordinary thing I had ever witnessed in real time while my cameras were rolling.'\", \"from\": 3056, \"to\": 3217, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Celine was diagnosed in 2022 with the illness,which affects the central nervous systemand is said to turn people into 'human statues'.\", \"from\": 3219, \"to\": 3353, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the pain it causes, the singer vowed she would return to the stage for her fans: 'If I can not run, I will walk.\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3475, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If I can not walk, I will crawl.\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 3508, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I will not stop.'\", \"from\": 3509, \"to\": 3530, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Struggling with thinning or dull hair?\", \"from\": 3532, \"to\": 3570, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Experts say the real issue starts at your scalp  Mother's Day gifts for new mums and mums\\u2011to\\u2011be under \\u00a350  The oral\\u2011care gadget making waves thanks to its powerful clean  Dunelm's new outdoor collection will get your garden spring-ready - from just \\u00a33  The exact blush Margot Robbie wore in Wuthering Heights and best budget alternatives  metro.co.ukhas reached out to Celine's representatives for comment.\", \"from\": 3571, \"to\": 3977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3742, \"end\": 3748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durham_University\", \"score\": 0.9999999996844053, \"rank\": 3.155999512526117e-10, \"text\": \"Dunelm\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durham_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durham_University\"}, {\"begin\": 3840, \"end\": 3853, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margot_Robbie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Margot Robbie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margot_Robbie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margot_Robbie\"}, {\"begin\": 3862, \"end\": 3879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wuthering_Heights\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.178341767945026e-31, \"text\": \"Wuthering Heights\", \"types\": [\"Q571\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wuthering_Heights\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wuthering_Heights\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Got a story?\", \"from\": 3979, \"to\": 3991, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you have got